'''= "a local cryptoliberation community center".''' (in Vienna and elsewhere)

URL = https://www.parallele.at/


=Description=

""We are a small group of sovereign citizens based in Vienna who, after participating in events at Parallelní Polis, have decided to establish a local cryptoliberation community center for our peers and those who are curious and want to learn about cryptoanarchist arts, science, and technology. We are currently located in an 80m2 coworking space in the 18th district, and are expanding to a 230m2 location. We also have secured a public event space in Q21 Vienna’s MuseumsQuartier, called RaumD. To this end, we have a weekly meetup every Tuesday evening from 6-11pm."

